subject: Attn : Honorable Beneficiary
body:
Attn : Honorable Beneficiary .
Reference to the directives issued to this great financial agency, this agency wants to know if you have received your fund. If yes, can you as a matter of urgency confirm the transfer code to this agency for clarity and for further advice.
Threat as a matter of urgency to avoid any costly mistake.
Best Regards,
Mr. Canise Adams.

subject: Re:   Attn : Honorable Beneficiary
body:
Hello Mr. Canise Adams, thank you for reaching out. I appreciate your concern regarding the fund transfer. Could you please provide more details about the directives issued by the financial agency? I want to make sure everything is clear before confirming any transfer code. Thank you.

Best wishes,
Diane
